<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.9.2">
<l>varuka varuka varuka viṅkē</l>
<l rend="indent">vāmaṉa nampī. varuka viṅkē</l>
<l>kariya kuḻalceyya vāymu kattuk</l>
<l rend="indent">kākutta nampī. varuka viṅkē</l>
<l>ariya ṉivaṉeṉak kiṉṟu naṅkāy</l>
<l rend="indent">añcaṉa vaṇṇā vacala kattār</l>
<l>paripavam pēcat tarikka killēṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">pāviyē ṉukkiṅkē pōta rāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Come! Come! Please come here!</l>
<l rend="indent">Prince Vāmaṉa! Please come here!</l>
<l>Prince Kākutstha, with [your] black curls,</l>
<l rend="indent">red lips, and face, please come here!</l>
<l>Ladies! [Even] now, to me he is precious.</l>
<l>Kohl coloured [Lord]! I cannot bear it</l>
<l rend="indent">when those in the neighbourhood spew scorn.</l>
<l>Ah! Come here to poor me!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
